Enjoy a new experience with the revamped Octopus App!

There’s a brand new home screen for the Octopus App, separating the functions of Octopus card and Octopus Wallet (formerly O! ePay), so you can easily find the services you need!

The wide range of services in Octopus App include:

Octopus Card Services – for all your transport and retail payment needs

- Check and collect consumption vouchers, and view the cumulative eligible spending and spending records;

- Add and Top Up Octopus on iPhone or Apple Watch
Add an Octopus card to your iPhone or Apple Watch with just a few steps. Top up anytime, anywhere on Octopus App with your Octopus Wallet, bank account with Faster Payment System (FPS) or using Apple Pay with your favourite credit or debit/ATM card without service fees;

- Top up your own Octopus cards, your family’s or even your friend’s, without touching any cash;

- Check and collect Public Transport Fare Subsidies, and purchase MTR, KMB and First Ferry monthly passes in a breeze;

- Manage your daily expenses with ease by checking the remaining value and spending records of your Octopus with a summary by categories.

Octopus Wallet Services – for managing your other daily expense needs

- Transfer money from your bank account
Sign up for FPS Electronic Direct Debit Authorisation to instantly transfer money from your bank account into Octopus Wallet (the “Wallet”) for everyday use;

- Shop globally at online merchants accepting Mastercard, while enjoying peace of mind with the Wallet’s prepaid balance;

- Get Octopus UnionPay Card instantly to make QR code payments with your mobile on the Mainland and around the globe;

- Send money to payee’s Octopus Wallet, Octopus cards or bank accounts (via FPS) with ease;

- Pay with Octopus to enjoy fabulous offers and rewards at popular merchants.

Octopus Card Image Store

- Style your Octopus on Mobile with your favourite card image


For more details, please visit www.octopus.com.hk/octopusapp

